#, fuzzy
msgid "learn more."
msgstr "ddysgu rhagor"

#: incompatibleCheck.title
msgid "Checking Add-on Compatibility"
msgstr "Gwirio Cytunedd yr Ychwanegyn"

#: incompatibleCheck.label
msgid "Looking for newer versions of your add-ons…"
msgstr "Chwilio am fersiwn mwy diweddar o'ch ychwanegion…"

#: clickHere.label
msgid "View more information about this update"
msgstr "Darllen mwy am y diweddariad"

#: evangelism.desc
msgid ""
"It is strongly recommended that you apply this \n"
"update for &brandShortName; as soon as possible."
msgstr ""
"Argymhellir yn gryf eich bod yn diweddaru &brandShortName; \n"
"gynted ag y bo modd."

#: license.instructions
msgid ""
"If you agree to the terms of this agreement, click I Agree \n"
"below to continue installing this update."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych yn cytuno ag amodau'r cytundeb, cliciwch Cytuno \n"
"isod i barhau i osod y diweddariad."

#: license.titleText
msgid "Software License Agreement"
msgstr "Cytundeb Trwydded Meddalwedd"

#: license.introText
msgid "Terms and conditions for using this software."
msgstr "Amodau defnyddio'r feddalwedd."

#: license.instructionText
msgid ""
"Please read the following license agreement. Use the scroll bar to view the "
"rest of this agreement."
msgstr ""
"Darllenwch y cytundeb trwyddedu canlynol. Defnyddiwch y bar sgrolio i "
"ddarllen gweddill y cytundeb."

#: license.accept
msgid "I accept the terms of the License Agreement"
msgstr "Rwy'n Derbyn amodau’r Cytundeb Trwyddedu"

#: license.accept.accesskey
msgid "c"
msgstr "c"

#: license.decline
msgid "I do NOT accept the terms of the License Agreement"
msgstr "NID wyf yn derbyn amodau'r Cytundeb Trwyddedu"

#: license.decline.accesskey
msgid "T"
msgstr "T"

#: incompatibleList.title
msgid "Incompatible Add-ons Found"
msgstr "Wedi Canfod Ychwanegion Anghytûn"

#: downloadPage.title
msgid "Downloading &brandShortName;"
msgstr "Llwytho &brandShortName; i lawr"

#: downloading.intro
msgid "Downloading the update…"
msgstr "Llwytho'r diweddariad…"

#: connecting.label
msgid "Connecting to the update server…"
msgstr "Cysylltu á'r gweinydd diweddaru…"

#: verificationFailedText.label
msgid ""
"&brandShortName; was unable to verify the integrity of the \n"
"incremental update it downloaded, so it is now downloading \n"
"the complete update package."
msgstr ""
"Nid oedd &brandShortName; yn gallu gwirio integriad y \n"
"diweddariad cynyddol mae wedi ei lwytho, felly mae'n \n"
"llwytho'r pecyn diweddaru cyfan."

#: viewDetails.tooltip
msgid "View details for this update"
msgstr "Gweld manylion y diweddariad"

#: details.link
msgctxt "details.link"
msgid "Details"
msgstr "Manylion"

#: error.title
msgid "Update Failed"
msgstr "Methodd y Diweddariad"

#: error.label
msgid ""
"There were problems checking for, downloading, or installing this \n"
"update. &brandShortName; could not be updated because:"
msgstr ""
"Bu anawsterau wrth lwytho neu osod y diweddariad. Nid oedd \n"
"modd diweddaru &brandShortName; oherwydd:"

#: errorManual.label
msgid ""
"You can update &brandShortName; manually by visiting this link \n"
"and downloading the latest version:"
msgstr ""
"Gallwch ddiweddaru &brandShortName; gyda llaw drwy ymweld \n"
"â'r dolenni a llwytho'r fersiwn diweddaraf:"

#: errorpatching.intro
msgid ""
"The partial Update could not be applied. \n"
"&brandShortName; will try again by downloading a complete Update."
msgstr ""
"Nid oedd modd gosod y Diweddariad rhannol. \n"
"Bydd &brandShortName; yn ceisio eto drwy lwytho'r Diweddariad cyfan."

#: genericBackgroundError.label
msgid ""
"&brandShortName; is unable to determine if there is an update available. "
"Please \n"
"make sure that you have the latest version of &brandShortName; from:"
msgstr ""
"Mae &brandShortName; yn methu pennu a oes diweddariad ar gael. \n"
"Gwnewch yn siŵr fod fersiwn diweddaraf o &brandShortName; gennych o:"

#: errorCertAttrNoUpdate2.label
msgid ""
"Something is preventing &brandShortName; from updating securely. \n"
"Please make sure that you have the latest version of &brandShortName; from:"
msgstr ""
"Mae rhywbeth yn atal &brandShortName; rhag diweddaru'n ddiogel. \n"
"Gwnewch yn siŵr fod fersiwn diweddaraf o &brandShortName; gennych o:"

#: errorCertAttrHasUpdate.label
msgid ""
"Something is trying to trick &brandShortName; into accepting an \n"
"insecure update. Please contact your network provider and seek help."
msgstr ""
"Mae rhywbeth yn ceisio twyllo &brandShortName; i dderbyn \n"
"diweddariad anniogel. Cysylltwch â'ch darparwr rhwydwaith er mwyn cael "
"cymorth."

#: finishedPage.title
msgid "Update Ready to Install"
msgstr "Diweddariad yn Barod i'w Osod"

#: finishedPage.text
msgctxt "finishedPage.text"
msgid ""
"The update will be installed the next time &brandShortName; starts. You \n"
"can restart &brandShortName; now, or continue working and restart later."
msgstr ""
"Bydd y diweddariad yn cael ei osod y tro nesaf y bydd &brandShortName; yn "
"cychwyn. \n"
"Mae modd ailgychwyn &brandShortName; nawr, neu barhau i weithio ac "
"ailgychwyn yn hwyrach."

#: finishedBackgroundPage.text
msgid ""
"A security and stability update for &brandShortName; has been \n"
"downloaded and is ready to be installed."
msgstr ""
"Mae diweddariad diogelwch a sefydlogrwydd ar gyfer &brandShortName; \n"
"wedi ei lwytho i lawr ac mae'n barod i'w osod."

#: finishedBackground.name
